+### Region, +, +The `cloud.aws.region` can be set to a region and will automatically use the relevant settings for both `ec2` and `s3`. The available values are: `us-east` (`us-east-1`), `us-west` (`us-west-1`), `us-west-1`, `us-west-2` `ap-southeast` (`ap-southeast-1`), `ap-northeast` (`ap-northeast-1`) `eu-west` (`eu-west-1`)., +, +, +## EC2 Discovery, +, +ec2 discovery allows to use the ec2 APIs to perform automatic discovery (similar to multicast in non hostile multicast environments). Here is a simple sample configuration:, +, +    cloud:, +        aws:, +            access_key: AKVAIQBF2RECL7FJWGJQ, +            secret_key: vExyMThREXeRMm/b/LRzEB8jWwvzQeXgjqMX+6br, +    , +    discovery:, +        type: ec2, +]